cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.CR 

The paper deals with statistical analysis and algorithms for adaptively chosen queries, which are common topics in machine learning and data science. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses differential privacy, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper involves statistical analysis, which is a common topic in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
